@startuml Project Creation Activity
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam roundcorner 10

title Project Creation - Activity Diagram

start

:Department Manager creates project;
:Enter project details (name, description);
:Set start date;
:Set budget (optional);
:Assign to department;

if (Project manager assigned?) then (yes)
  :Assign project manager;
  if (Manager in department?) then (yes)
    :Continue;
  else (no)
    :Display error;
    stop
  endif
else (no)
  :Continue;
endif

:Validate project name (unique);
if (Name unique?) then (yes)
  :Save project;
  :Set status: Planning;
  :Generate project ID;
else (no)
  :Display error: Name exists;
  stop
endif

partition "Project Setup" {
  :Create project folder;
  :Set up project structure;
  :Assign initial team members;
  :Create initial tasks;
}

:Update status: Active;
:Notify team members;
:Complete project creation;

stop

note right
  **Business Rules:**
  - Project name must be unique
  - Project manager must be in same department
  - Department must exist
  - Start date is required
end note

@enduml

